name: maintenance, transmission network, electricity, high voltage direct current aerial line | maintenance, transmission network, electricity, high voltage direct current aerial line | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/26206/documentation

This dataset represents the maintenance of 1 km and year of an high voltage direct current arieal line (FeAl conductor at 250/350 kV).;;;Literature data given for the entire lifetime per km was divided by lifetime (40 a) to get yearly values. ;Source: Jorge, R., Hawkins, T.R., Hertwich, E..G (2012): Life cycle assessment of electricity transmission and distribution - part 1: power lines and cables. Int J Life Cycle Assess 17: 9-15. supplementary matierial p.12, table S10.

Manufacture and replacement of parts

Decommissioning and disposal of parts
category: F:Construction/42:Civil engineering/422:Construction of utility projects/4220:Construction of utility projects

processDocumentation.timeDescription: refers to publication date of literature sources
processDocumentation.geographyDescription: The scope of the underlying literature source is Europe.
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: Maintenance is comprised of the replacement of parts
